quran[5{c,v,t}:
2,265,"bakhalaaf iss ke jo lau g apne maal mehez Allah ki Raza joi ke liye dil ke poooray Sabaat o qarar ke sath kharch karte hain, un ke kharch ki misaal aisi hai, jaisay kisi satah murtafa par aik baagh ho agar zor ki baar sh ho jaye to do gina phal laaye, aur agar zor ki barish nah bhi ho to aik halki phwaar hi uss ke liye kaafi ho jaye tum jo kuch karte ho, sab Allah ki nazar mein hai"
2,266,"kya tum mein se koi yeh pasand karta hai ke is ke paas aik hara bhara baagh ho, nﮦron se sairaab, khajoron aur angarro aur hrqsm ke phalon se lada howa, aur woh ain uss waqt aik taiz bagoole ki zad mein aa kar jhulas jaye, jabkay woh khud boorha ho aur is ke kam sun bachay abhi kisi Laiq nah hon? is terhan Allah apni baatein tumahray samnay bayan karta hai, shayad ke tum ghhor o fikar karo"
2,267,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jo maal tum ne kamaye hain aur jo kuch hum ne zameen se tumahray liye nikala hai, uss se behtar hissa raah khuda mein kharch karo aisa nah ho ke is ki raah mein dainay ke liye buri se buri cheez chhantnay ki koshish karne lagu, halaank wohi cheez agar koi tumhe day, to tum hargiz ussay laina gawara nah karo ge ila yeh ke is ko qubool karne mein tum aghmaz bart jao tumhe jaan laina chahiye ke Allah be niaz hai aur behtareen sifaat se mutsif hai"
2,268,"shetan tumhe muflisi se darata hai aur sharamnaak tarz amal ikhtiyar karne ki targheeb deta hai, magar Allah tumhe apni bakhshish aur fazl ki umeed dilaata hai Allah bara farakh dast aur Dana hai"
2,269,"jis ko chahta hai hikmat ataa karta hai, aur jis ko hikmat mili, ussay haqeeqat mein barri doulat mil gayi inn baton se sirf wohi log sabaq letay hain, jo danishmand hain"
